{"type": "article", "id": 21051, "title": "化妆品包装设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-21T07:24:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104201qcJnCdkofwx4mYXB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套香水、乳液和香皂的包装设计，来自希腊，是专门卖给游客的。4 套产品分别结合了 4 种气味，柑橘、无花果、莲花和海浪，并对应了黄、粉、白、蓝 4 种颜色，清新明媚。不同的元素都画成了形象的图案，用相近的颜色区别，颜色都很亮丽，表现出当地的活泼热情。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150739Nvgi4Yb0xdr75lmB.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150739LpZXWbBUP73mrygx.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150740HYKyFM3NRgljnGt0.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150741fjbspcA1Eo2m8qZw.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"763\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}